perform actions in response to a change in the lifecycle status of another
component such activities , fragments ..


using these componenets we can move the code of depenedant components
out of the lifecycle method and into the comonents themselves !

!!!!!!!!!!!!
the "androidx.lifecycle" package provides classes and interfaces that 
let you build lifecycle aware compoenents 
which are elements that can adjust their behavior based on the current
status of the followed component !

lifecycles are managed by the OS

Lifecycle is a class that holds the informations about the lifecycle of a
a componenet !

